Title: Notice Regarding the Anomalous Behaviors of the "Dormant Tacet Discord" Underneath the Mine
Text:
Lately the "dormant Tacet Discord" displays strange activities. Multiple incidents of miners missing have happend and are under investigation.
You are advised to strictly follow the Security Regulations for Operations at the mines of Tiger's Maw to ensure the safety of yourselves and everyone around.
Safety is everything. Do not follow any unidentified cries for help.
Midnight Rangers have sent out teams for investigation. The cause of the anomalies will soon be clear,
